{"tid":371420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"水浸橋龍珠島變孤島　居民玩命揸車「渡海」","createTime":"2017-08-23T16:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T03:15:06.000Z","uid":22675,"like":160,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e85832ae08d35c0ef84fb1dff89f183f6acab3e5","tid":371420,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170823/photo/bkn-20170823170541611-0823_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170823204749\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170823%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170823170541611-0823_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170823204749&h=63d702e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n08月23日(三) 17:05   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打風被困龍珠島，勇司機私家車當潛水艇闖水浸橋！今日風暴期間全港多區嚴重水浸，屯門龍珠島連接黃金海岸的徑青龍路行車橋，同樣被洪水淹沒，不斷有海浪湧上橋面，完全未能看見路面。出市區的唯一通道水浸，令龍珠島變成孤島，居民無法出入。<br />\n<br />\n不過竟有居民無論如何都要硬闖，據網上流傳的片段所見，最少兩輛私家車曾經強行「渡海」，其中一名男司機駕駛私家車接載最少兩名男女親友，由龍珠島駕車經行車橋駛出黃金海岸，上橋前司機向友人稱：「都係要去㗎啦，預備喇！」然後踩油衝出，積水幾乎完全蓋過車頭的行車橋，遠看私家車如在海中行駛，期間兩邊不斷有巨浪拍向車身，前方只見白茫茫一片，女乘客嚇至大叫：「唔好行啦，返去啦！」 <br />\n<br />\n不過男司機仍處之泰然，回應稱：「點退後呀姐姐！ONE WAY ONLY（只有一條路）！」最後私家車竟然安全無恙駛過行車橋，男司機則淡然道：「真係要搵啲嘢洗下架車呀。」 <br />\n<br />\n有黃金海岸高層的居民，從另一角度拍下私家車闖橋經過，場面更令人膽戰心驚，僅約200米的路程令人為之窒息，直至它安全渡過才鬆一口氣。"},{"pid":"26fb7f6bfc92077d5ffc70ae63c1e2db8ca62180","tid":371420,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2381d69b11e7c7c6d88fe2ff5d5a2d4609c449c","tid":371420,"uid":26752,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:37:33.000Z","msg":"ONE WAY ONLY<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b2d674c597353cd9e8678bc28a6bddca1982db","tid":371420,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82666fa6ec72cf7135394f0438c8df6d3482867a","tid":371420,"uid":6347,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:40:15.000Z","msg":"摩西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cffde36cd7b4aae07a2dae912d31daad56f51b6e","tid":371420,"uid":52358,"like":179,"dislike":0,"score":179,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:42:02.000Z","msg":"only one way out<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f70b960ee0c2007d60cbcff780a56f6ca2f911c","tid":371420,"uid":18638,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:42:29.000Z","msg":"Only one way out"},{"pid":"bc9046e58d0e8d333782e68eca8e452e3dee6808","tid":371420,"uid":124439,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:42:29.000Z","msg":"危險總會有的 你要做的就是駕駛風險而非迴避風險you know<br />\n<blockquote>ONE WAY ONLY<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9041cbe0229e5cf8fa95d206c962ae0c8cc29dc3","tid":371420,"uid":14244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:43:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>摩西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5fcbf896a7b56438aa613177a6ed6aba396709","tid":371420,"uid":124439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:44:09.000Z","msg":"today is good day"},{"pid":"2e246c1af481e41bd4e0f5d1e85a246495fd8549","tid":371420,"uid":34793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:45:46.000Z","msg":"型到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94da91d8daef62ef3cd814af2ab443b68a3f18bd","tid":371420,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T